				<wikidot:authorName>Pedantique</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3118444</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The tone feels pretty loose in this piece, especially in sentences like “SCP-3829 is resistant to most methods of death,” and I think it would benefit from a revision pass for more precise wording. I think I get the general idea of what’s going on, but I don’t think the article benefits from that generality.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
