				<wikidot:authorName>Mortos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1705184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is brave, as without the context of 3731 it feels very random. I <em>have</em> read 3731 and therefore enjoyed this one (along with the idea that there might be more from that canon, considering the ending), but I shall have to think about whether or not I want to upvote an article that relies so heavily on another to make sense.</p> 
				 	]]>
